data.description: Stunning California Split! This house has it all. Spacious vauled ceilings, open floorplan that is perfect for entertaining. Finished basement AND finished Sub basement offering plenty of functional living space. Large Bedrooms and Living Spaces. Open kitchen and dining area. HUGE corner lot with Privacy Fence situated in a quiet culdesac. Highly sought after neighborhood. This is a wonderfully maintained move in ready home that will not disappoint.
